HOME RUN DERBY is an exciting simulation of an all-time home run
hitting contest.  It takes a good eye and a lot of practice to be
able to hit the long ball consistently.  Good Luck.

Home Run Derby is shareware.  The few dollars you paid for this
shareware version goes does not go to the author.  It is simply the
modest fee you pay to try the software.  You are free to evaluate
this software.  If you like it or find it useful, you must register
